// Path config, set by site_render() from the arguments the magusfile passes in - the
// generator does not hardcode where the workspace, docs, or output live, so it stays
// a config-agnostic library rather than owning project layout the caller reaches into.
// Pico CSS is vendored at assets/pico.min.css (copied to gen/assets/ on each generate).
// Same-origin; served from this site, never fetched remotely. Version: @picocss/pico@2.1.1.
// SRI provenance (for reference, not used with same-origin link):
//   sha384-L1dWfspMTHU/ApYnFiMz2QID/PlP1xCW9visvBdbEkOLkSSWsP6ZJWhPw6apiXxU
// To upgrade: download the new pico.min.css into assets/ (not gen/assets/), update the
// version comment, recompute the SRI if ever reverting to CDN delivery, and regenerate.
// GH / SITE_URL / SITE_DESC are in render_types.buzz (shared config the writer
// modules also need).


// Value objects. They must precede Site, which holds arrays of them - Buzz has no
// forward references to types.

// loadMeta/assetIntegrityCheck/orphanCheck/capture/buildCommits (+ HISTORY_MAX) moved to
// render_gates.buzz (the build-correctness + provenance layer).


// isGenerated/outputName/climb/climbFromDir/sitePathPrefix/newCleanDirectory moved to
// render_route.buzz (path/URL routing helpers).















// CSP construction and content hashing are in render_csp.buzz (flat-imported
// above): fileSha256, scriptHash, extractInlineScripts, computeCSP,
// cspForRedirectStub, and the CSP_* constants.



